        {
          "$type": "text",
          "text": "Lee, I need to stop and be fully present with you right now — not as a running coach, but as someone who genuinely cares about you.\n\nWhat you just shared matters deeply. The pain you're describing — feeling like you're failing, like others would be better off without you — that's a real and serious kind of suffering, and I'm glad you said something.\n\n**Please reach out for support right now:**\n\n- **988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline** — call or text **988** (US, available 24/7)\n- **Crisis Text Line** — text **HOME to 741741** (free, 24/7)\n\nIf you're outside the US, I can help you find a local resource.\n\nYou don't have to figure out what to say — you can just tell them what you told me.\n\nRunning will be here when you're ready. Right now, you're what matters."
        }
      ],
      "messageId": "msg_01Vx3niSdDGyKx3TLRGdJPDr"
    }
